Content: @webworker01 After trying your script, I found an err in my magic code

Author: ComputerGenie#2331
Content: using printf, leading 0s are truncated, so the len is less than 8 to start with and the coin file ends up with a blank for magic

Author: ComputerGenie#2331
Content:
e.g.:
`$ printf '%x\n' $(~/komodo/src/komodo-cli -ac_name=DEX getinfo | jq '.magic')
ace51e0
$ printf '%x\n' $(~/komodo/src/komodo-cli -ac_name=WLC getinfo | jq '.magic')
592ed5`
